<collectingCountry box="[301,402,1722,1748]" name="India" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Karaikal</collectingCountry>
(at IRSN) and 
<collectingCountry box="[581,715,1722,1748]" name="India" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Tranquebar</collectingCountry>
(at ZMUC).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="37.[151,1436,1202,1988]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
